			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Blaize Clement</strong></span> has written psychology books and textbooks, essays, short stories, and a play. She recently completed a historical novel, and is currently working on a memoir about her quest for healing. She lives in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.</p><a href="/contributors/blaize-clement" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
